divs: Sighting DetailsMyself and my partner went to Wollongong Harbour to view the waves from a storm we were having it was winding and dark , we were taking photos of the people in wet suits braving the waves when we captured the object. We didn't see it at the time only when we returned home to view the pics on our computer. I believe that we are not alone and excited if its what it looks like.
Summary: watching waves at the harbour and took photos, noticed strange light upon returning home
